---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
// Add all your images here
import howItWorks1 from '../assets/howitworks1.jpg';
import howItWorks2 from '../assets/howitworks2.jpg';
import howItWorks3 from '../assets/howitworks3.jpg';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="How It Works | New Leaf Academy" description="Our simple, supportive process for starting your tutoring journey with New Leaf Academy." />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>How It Works</h1>
			<p class="intro-text">
				Starting your journey with us is simple, transparent, and designed to ensure the perfect fit for your child. Hereâ€™s a step-by-step look at our process, from our first chat to ongoing success. We know no family or child is the same, so we are flexible and ready to adapt our process to fit your needs.
			</p>

			<div class="process-grid">
				<div class="process-row">
					<div class="steps-column">
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">1</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Initial Contact</h3>
								<p>Reach out to Dan via our consultation form, email, or phone. He will guide you through the process and answer any initial questions.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">2</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Discovery Chat</h3>
								<p>He'll offer to schedule a friendly, informal chat to discuss your child's specific needs, learning style, and academic goals in detail.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="image-column">
            {/* === Image 1: Load Eagerly === */}
						<Image
              src={howItWorks1}
              alt="A student engaged in an online tutoring session"
              class="process-image"
              format="webp"      {/* Add */}
              quality={70}        {/* Add */}
              loading="eager"     {/* Add */}
              sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 600px, 0px" {/* Add */}
			  decoding="async"
            />
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-row">
					<div class="image-column">
            {/* === Image 2: Load Eagerly === */}
						<Image
              src={howItWorks2}
              alt="A tutor explaining a concept on a whiteboard"
              class="process-image"
              format="webp"      {/* Add */}
              quality={70}        {/* Add */}
              loading="eager"          {/* Add */}
              sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 600px, 0px" {/* Add */}
			  decoding="async"
            />
					</div>
					<div class="steps-column">
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">3</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Free Taster Session</h3>
								<p>We'll book in a 30-minute taster session. This is a great chance for your child to meet their tutor and experience their teaching style firsthand, with no obligation to continue.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">4</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Tailored Learning Plan</h3>
								<p>After the taster session, we'll work with you to decide on the best course of action and create a plan tailored to your child's goals.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-row">
					<div class="steps-column">
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">5</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Regular Tutoring Sessions</h3>
								<p>With a plan in place, regular one-to-one sessions will begin, focusing on building knowledge, skills, and confidence in a supportive environment. Your child will be encouraged to lead sessions by picking topics they struggle with.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<div class="step-number">6</div>
							<div class="step-content">
								<h3>Ongoing Support & Feedback</h3>
								<p>You'll have direct contact for the tutor and be able to ask questions about progress anytime. If you feel the focus of sessions ever needs to change, the tutor is always ready to adapt.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="image-column">
            {/* === Image 3: Load Lazily === */}
						<Image
              src={howItWorks3}
              alt="A student and tutor celebrating a success"
              class="process-image"
              format="webp"      {/* Add */}
              quality={70}        {/* Add */}
              loading="lazy"      {/* Add */}
              sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 600px, 0px" {/* Add */}
			  decoding="async"
            />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<h2>Still Need Help?</h2>
				<p>Our expert tutors are ready to provide the one-to-one support your child needs. Book a free consultation to get started today!</p>
				<a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
					Book Your Free Consultation and Taster Session
				</a>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
		--box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 2em auto;
		padding: 0 1em;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		color: var(--accent-light);
	}

	h1, .intro-text {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--accent-light)
	}

	.intro-text {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto 3em;
		font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
	}

	.steps-column {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5em;
	}

	.step {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5em;
	}

	.step-number {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 50px;
		height: 50px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background-color: var(--accent);
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.2em;
		z-index: 1;
		border: 4px solid #fff;
	}

	.step-content {
		background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
		padding: 1.5em;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	.step-content h3 {
		color: var(--accent);
		margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
		font-size: clamp(1.3em, 3vw, 1.5em);
	}

	.step-content p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	
	.image-column {
		display: none; /* Hide images on mobile by default */
	}

	.process-row {
		margin-bottom: 3em;
	}

	/* --- DESKTOP LAYOUT --- */
	@media (min-width: 1024px) {
		.process-row {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 3em;
		}

		.image-column {
			display: block; /* Show images on desktop */
			padding: 1em;
		}

		/* This makes the second row reverse its column order */
		.process-row:nth-child(2) .image-column {
			order: -1;
		}

		.process-image {
			width: 100%;
			height: auto;
			border-radius: 12px;
			box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		}
	}

	.cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin: 4em auto 0;
		padding: 2.5em;
		background-color: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		color: var(--accent);
		max-width: 900px;
	}
	
	.cta-section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.cta-section p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1em 2em;
		background-color: var(--accent-pop);
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}
</style>